---
Source:
  ID: 8147df67-439b-4909-bfe3-d55b944af666
Description: November 11
By: Hafiz
Title: Beautiful Hands
---
This is the kind of Friend you are：

Without making me realize my soul’s anguished history,

you slip into my house at night and, while I am sleeping,

you silently carry off all my suffering and sordid past in your beautiful
hands.
